author: desruisseaux
msg: ISO 19162 requires that we replace non-ASCII characters by ASCII ones for all WKT elements except REMARKS["..."].
Note that we make an exception to this rule when formatting a WKT using the SIS-specific Convention.INTERNAL mode.
